     <body>
           <div type="panelGrp" xml:id="eg_0001">
              <cbml:panel n="1" characters="#mafalda #father">
                 <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#mafalda">
                    DECIME, ¿QUIÉN 
                    ES ESTE PETISO
                    TODO EMPON-
                    CHADO?
                 </cbml:balloon>
                 <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#father">
                    ES NAPOLEÓN,
                    CUANDO INVA-
                    DIÓ RUSIA         
                 </cbml:balloon> 
                 <note type="panelDesc"> Mafalda and her father are chatting in the living
                    room. Mafalda is showing him a page from a book. He looks at it while
                    sitting on a chair and holding a folded newspaper. 
                 </note> 
              </cbml:panel>
              <cbml:panel n="2" characters="#mafalda #father">
                 <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#mafalda"> 
                    <emph rendition="#b #large">
                       ¿RUSIA? INVADIÓ 
                       RUSIA?
                    </emph>
                 </cbml:balloon>
                 <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#father">
                    AJHÁ                    
                 </cbml:balloon>
                 <note type="panelDesc"> Mafalda's eyes and mouth are wide open in amazement.
                    Her father is back to reading the newspaper, which now covers his face. 
                 </note> 
              </cbml:panel>
              <cbml:panel n="3" characters="#mafalda">
                 <cbml:balloon type="thought" who="#mafalda">   
                    ¡SALUTE!                  
                 </cbml:balloon>      
                 <note type="panelDesc"> MCU of Mafalda's head as she covers her mouth and
                    stares in thoughtful pose. 
                 </note> 
              </cbml:panel>
              <cbml:panel n="4" characters="#mafalda #father">              
              <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#mafalda">
                 ¡OTRA QUE 
                 GOLDWATER!
              </cbml:balloon>
                 <fw type="sig" place="lower-right">
                    QUINO
                 </fw>
              <note type="panelDesc"> WS of Mafalda and her father in the living room. 
                 Mafalda's eyes are once again wide open in amazement. She holds the closed
                 book in her left hand and touches her chin with the right. Her father has
                 put down the newspaper again and stares ahead in confusion or amazement. 
              </note>  
           </cbml:panel>
              <note type="bibl">
                 27 octubre ‘64
              </note> 
        </div>        
        <div type="panelGrp" xml:id="eg_0002">             
              <cbml:panel n="1" characters="#father #mother">
              <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#father"> 
                 ¡LA VERDAD ES QUE ESTOS   <lb/>
                 CHINOS PODRÍAN DEJARSE   <lb/>
                 DE MACANAS!
              </cbml:balloon>
                 <note type="panelDesc"> WS of Mafalda's parents in the living room. Father
                    is sitting and reading the newspaper as he comments. Mother sews in the
                    backgroung on the right of the frame. 
                 </note> 
              </cbml:panel> 
              <cbml:panel n="2" characters="#mafalda #father #mother">           
              <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#mafalda">
                 <emph rendition="#b #extra_large">
                 ¡BOOM!
                 </emph>
              </cbml:balloon>
              <note type="panelDesc"> WS shows Mafalda making a loud explosion noise in
                 the living room as her father scrambles for cover and her mother looks
                 from the background with big, shocked eyes. 
              </note>
           </cbml:panel>
           <cbml:panel n="3" characters="#father #mother #mafalda">           
           <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#mafalda">                 
                 ¡PSICOSIS COLECTIVA!
           </cbml:balloon> 
              <fw type="sig" place="lower-right">
                 QUINO
              </fw>
           <note type="panelDesc"> WS of the living room. Mafalda walks out toward the right
              of the frame while her parents watch from the left with an angry expression. 
           </note>                  
           </cbml:panel>
           <note type="bibl">
              27 octubre ‘64
           </note>
        </div>
        <div type="panelGrp" xml:id="eg_0003"> 
           <cbml:panel n="1" characters="#father">
              <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#father"> 
                 ¡NO HAY COMO UN BUEN HOBBY   <lb/>
                 PARA OLVIDARSE DEL MUNDO Y  <lb/>
                 SUS PROBLEMAS!                 
              </cbml:balloon>                   
              <note type="panelDesc"> WS shows father spraying his plants on his knees. He
                 is smiling and look very calm.
              </note>                           
           </cbml:panel>
           <cbml:panel n="2" characters="#father">
              <sound rendition="#b #large"> 
                 ¡CHIST!
              </sound>                       
              <note type="panelDesc"> Father hears a sound and turns his head 
                 to look behind him.                
              </note>              
           </cbml:panel>
           <cbml:panel n="3" characters="#father #mafalda">
              <note type="panelDesc"> OSS shows Mafalda from behind her father's head. 
                 She is stretching her eyes and smiling, as if to look Asian. 
              </note> 
           </cbml:panel>
           <cbml:panel n="4" characters="#father">                
              <note type="panelDesc"> WS shows father sitting among his plants with extra wide
                 eyes giving him a nervous and worried look. He still holds the spray pump 
                 in his right hand, and is holding his head with his left. 
              </note>            
           <fw type="sig" place="lower-right">
              QUINO
           </fw>                  
           </cbml:panel>
           <note type="bibl">
              3 noviembre ‘64
           </note>
        </div>    
        <div type="panelGrp" xml:id="eg_0004"> 
           <cbml:panel n="1" characters="#mafalda #father">
              <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#mafalda">  
                 ¡DAME PARA  <lb/>
                 CARAMELOS!  <lb/>
                 ¡ANDÁ, CHE,  <lb/>
                 VAMOS! 
              </cbml:balloon>
              <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#father"> 
                 ¡NO, PORQUE  <lb/>
                 DESPUÉS NO  <lb/>
                 COMÉS!
              </cbml:balloon> 
              <note type="panelDesc"> WS of Mafalda standing behind her father with a demanding
                 look and extending her palm. Her father stands in front of the mirror while he
                 shaves with an electric shaver. 
              </note>
           </cbml:panel>
           <cbml:panel n="2" characters="#mafalda #father">
              <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#mafalda">  
                 ¡ASÍ ES LA COSA! TOTAL… UN  <lb/>
                 DÍA LOS CHINOS SE LEVANTAN   <lb/>
                 ATRAVESADOS  <lb/>
                 Y ¡PATAPÚM!
              </cbml:balloon>
              <note type="panelDesc"> WS shows Mafalda speaking with her arms open. Her
                 father glances back at her while he continues shaving. 
              </note> 
           </cbml:panel>
           <cbml:panel n="3" characters="#mafalda #father">
              <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#mafalda"> 
                 …Y UNA POBRE NENITA DEJA   <lb/>
                 ESTE MUNDO CON  <lb/>
                 LA AMARGURA  <lb/>
                 DE QUE LE NE-  <lb/>
                 GARAN UNOS   <lb/>
                 INOCENTES  <lb/>
                 CARAMELOS!
              </cbml:balloon>
              <note type="panelDesc"> WS shows Mafalda with a dramatic and sad face. Her
                 right hand now rests on her chest. Her father has interrupted his shave
                 and now has wide eyes indicative of a perplexed expression. 
              </note>
           </cbml:panel>
           <cbml:panel n="4" characters="#mafalda">
              <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#mafalda"> 
                 FRANCAMENTE, NO VEO   <lb/>
                 QUE LOS CHINOS SEAN  <lb/>
                 TAN ABOMINABLES.
           </cbml:balloon>
           <fw type="sig" place="lower-right">
              QUINO
           </fw>
              <note type="panelDesc"> Panel shows Mafalda sitting with a happy and satisfied
                 look on her face as she licks her lips among candy and wrappers. 
              </note>
           </cbml:panel>               
           <note type="bibl">
                 3 noviembre ‘64
           </note>            
        </div>
        <pb/>    
      </body>
      </text>
